SingleHop,is,a,server,and,cloud,hosting,service,They,offer,dedicated,servers,private,and,public,cloud,hosting,and,an,array,of,managed,hosting,services,The,SingleHop,API,enables,users,to,build,applications,to,interact,and,exchange,data,with,the,server,management,ticketing,and,billing,systems,The,API,uses,REST,calls,and,will,return,JSON,The,service,requires,an,account,and,an,API,key,for,access,and,features,over,API,calls